.el .ds Aq '
.TH SM-STATS 1  "stats " 
.SH NAME
stats \- Show workspace or client statistics
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBstats\fR [\fB\-\-all\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fICLIENT\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Show workspace or client statistics
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-all\fR
Aggregate across all known workspaces
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
[\fICLIENT\fR]
Client name for per\-client stats
